    tmp = 0.45
    v2 = wp.sin((wp.cos(tmp + 0.48) / wp.cos(v0 + 0.58)))
    tmp = wp.abs((tmp - wp.sin(v1 + 0.39)))
    v1 = (v1 - 0.56)
    v1 = v2
    v2 = wp.exp(wp.sin(v0))
    v0 = wp.exp(((v1 + 0.89 - v1 + 0.95) * (v0 + 0.19 / v2 + 0.40)))
